            "notes": "This deck focuses on aggressive gameplay with Zurgo Bellstriker as the commander. It includes a variety of burn spells, fast creatures, and direct damage cards to quickly chip away at the opponent's life total. The goal is to maintain pressure on the opponent and finish them off before they can stabilize. The deck also includes cards that prevent the opponent from gaining life or make it difficult for them to cast spells effectively. By staying proactive and maintaining a fast pace, the deck aims to overwhelm the opponent and secure victory through consistent damage output. Overall, the key concept of this deck is to be relentless in dealing damage and putting the opponent on the back foot."
